steps.name: Create new pipeline project with valid random name 'z7XjqPO4q5wkY3Z' and return to dashboard
Click 'New Item' on the Side Menu
Input the New Item name: z7XjqPO4q5wkY3Z
Click 'Save' button on the configuration page
Click on 'Jenkins' name icon on the header
Delete all Maven installations that were set on the Configuration page
Click on 'Manage Jenkins' link on the side menu
Click 'Global Tool Configuration' link in 'System Configuration' section
Delete all the Maven versions installed on the 'Global Configuration Page'
Click 'Save' button on the 'Global Configuration Page'
Click 'Global Tool Configuration' link in 'System Configuration' section
